## Controllers
- Use attribute routing; return appropriate HTTP status codes.

## Security
- Enforce authentication/authorization; validate inputs; avoid over-posting.

## Observability
- Centralize logging; correlate requests.

## Validation Checklist
- [ ] Routing and status codes correct
- [ ] AuthZ enforced; inputs validated
- [ ] Logs consistent and useful

